gwtupload.client
Interface IFileInput

All Superinterfaces:
com.google.gwt.event.dom.client.HasChangeHandlers, com.google.gwt.event.shared.HasHandlers
All Known Implementing Classes:
IFileInput.AnchorFileInput, IFileInput.BrowserFileInput, IFileInput.ButtonFileInput, IFileInput.LabelFileInput
public interface IFileInput
extends com.google.gwt.event.dom.client.HasChangeHandlers

Interface used by Uploaders to use and configure a customized file input. Widgets implementing this interface have to render a file input tag because it will be added to the form which is sent to the server. This interface has thought to let the user the option to create customizable panels for file inputs.
